sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant MB as Message Broker
    participant W1 as Worker 1
    participant W2 as Worker 2

    P->>MB: Publish message (job payload)
    MB-->>P: Acknowledge receipt
    MB->>MB: Persist message to queue

    W1->>MB: Poll for messages
    MB-->>W1: Deliver message (mark in-flight)
    W2->>MB: Poll for messages
    MB-->>W2: No messages available (locked by W1)

    W1->>W1: Process job
    alt Processing succeeds
        W1->>MB: ACK message
        MB->>MB: Remove message from queue
        W1-->>P: Job completed
    else Processing fails
        W1->>MB: NACK message
        MB->>MB: Return message to queue
        MB-->>W2: Deliver message to next available worker
        W2->>W2: Process job
        W2->>MB: ACK message
        MB->>MB: Remove message from queue
    end
